<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:12:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>潜在的中国救助方案提振情绪，亚洲股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-24/</link><description>亚洲股市周三上涨，因市场乐观地认为中国当局将为已跌至多年低点的股市提供支持，而日本央行的鹰派倾向提振了日元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>美联储观点推动美元徘徊在六周高位附近；日本央行推动日元小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-6-week-high-fed-view-yen-edges-up-after-boj-2024-01-24/</link><description>周三，美元兑主要货币徘徊在六周高点附近，因投资者强化了美联储在美国经济强劲的情况下不会急于降息的预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-6-week-high-fed-view-yen-edges-up-after-boj-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称武装部队将确保南海“畅通无阻、和平”的勘探</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-armed-forces-ensure-unimpeded-peaceful-exploration-south-china-2024-01-24/</link><description>马尼拉国防部长表示，随着菲律宾将重点转向对外防御，菲律宾武装部队将保证在该国专属经济区（EEZ）内“不受阻碍、和平”地勘探和开采自然资源。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:27:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-armed-forces-ensure-unimpeded-peaceful-exploration-south-china-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示欧盟“不公平”的电动汽车补贴调查可能会损害两国关系 - 彭博社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eus-unfair-ev-subsidies-probe-risks-damaging-ties-bloomberg-news-2024-01-24/</link><description>傅聪在接受彭博社采访时表示，中国驻欧盟大使称欧盟对中国电动汽车制造商国家补贴的调查“不公平”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eus-unfair-ev-subsidies-probe-risks-damaging-ties-bloomberg-news-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>图瓦卢部长预计将在大选后重新审视与台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tuvalu-expected-review-taiwan-ties-after-election-minister-2024-01-24/</link><description>图瓦卢财政部长 Seve Paeniu 告诉路透社，图瓦卢预计在周五选举后重新审视与台湾的外交关系，并补充说这个太平洋小岛国的选民希望国际社会为气候变化和发展提供更多财政支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tuvalu-expected-review-taiwan-ties-after-election-minister-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>投资者团体对尾矿坝落后者加大力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/investor-group-turns-up-heat-mining-tailings-dam-laggards-2024-01-24/</link><description>一群管理着超过 25 万亿美元的投资者表示，他们计划挑战尚未承诺尾矿坝最佳实践标准的矿业公司，并可能在即将举行的年度会议上投票反对管理层。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 00:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/investor-group-turns-up-heat-mining-tailings-dam-laggards-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员抵达台湾表达大选后支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-lawmakers-arrive-taiwan-post-election-show-support-2024-01-23/</link><description>美国众议院台湾核心小组领导人、共和党众议员马里奥·迪亚斯·巴拉特和民主党众议员阿米·贝拉办公室周二表示，他们已抵达台北，以表达对台湾大选的支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 22:57:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-lawmakers-arrive-taiwan-post-election-show-support-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：考验中港股反弹能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-23/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 22:03:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>吉尔吉斯斯坦与新疆边境发生5.67级余震</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/magnitude-567-aftershock-strikes-kyrgyzstan-xinjiang-border-2024-01-23/</link><description>德国地球科学研究中心（GFZ）表示，吉尔吉斯斯坦和新疆边境地区周三发生了 5.67 级地震，就在同一地区发生了 7.1 级地震的一天后。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 21:23:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/magnitude-567-aftershock-strikes-kyrgyzstan-xinjiang-border-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于罗纳尔多在迈阿密国际交锋前受伤，纳斯尔推迟了中国友谊赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-nassr-postpone-china-friendlies-ronaldo-injured-before-inter-miami-clash-2024-01-23/</link><description>沙特俱乐部周二表示，克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多(Cristiano Ronaldo)的纳斯尔(Al-Nassr)在前锋受伤后取消了两场中国之旅，这引发了人们对葡萄牙人参加即将对阵莱昂内尔·梅西(Lionel Messi)的迈阿密国际的比赛的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:26:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-nassr-postpone-china-friendlies-ronaldo-injured-before-inter-miami-clash-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于希望得到北京方面的支持，在美国上市的中国股市从低点反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-listed-china-stocks-bounce-off-lows-hopes-beijing-support-2024-01-23/</link><description>周二，在纽约上市的中国公司股票在经历了年初的低迷之后反弹，此前有关针对低迷的国内股市的救助计划的报道提振了市场情绪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 16:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-listed-china-stocks-bounce-off-lows-hopes-beijing-support-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>马云第四季度购买了价值 5000 万美元的阿里巴巴股票 - 纽约时报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/jack-ma-bought-alibaba-shares-worth-50-mln-fourth-quarter-nyt-2024-01-23/</link><description>据《纽约时报》周二报道，阿里巴巴联合创始人马云和董事长蔡崇信在第四季度购买了这家中国电子商务巨头价值数百万股的股票，导致该公司在美国上市的股价上涨约 7%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 15:23:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/jack-ma-bought-alibaba-shares-worth-50-mln-fourth-quarter-nyt-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫称中国船只不会在其海域进行研究</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-says-chinese-vessel-will-not-conduct-research-its-waters-2024-01-23/</link><description>马尔代夫外交部周二表示，一艘前往马尔代夫的中国科考船不会在印度洋群岛海域进行任何研究。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 14:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-says-chinese-vessel-will-not-conduct-research-its-waters-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>投资者放弃徒劳地等待中国修复经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/investors-give-up-futile-wait-china-fix-economy-2024-01-23/</link><description>从希望到犹豫，再到现在彻底投降，中国的全球投资者正纷纷撤离这个世界第二大经济体，并导致中国股市崩盘。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:55:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/investors-give-up-futile-wait-china-fix-economy-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔卡拉斯网球协会为墨尔本兹维列夫考试做准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tennis-alcaraz-gears-up-zverev-examination-melbourne-2024-01-23/</link><description>二号种子卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯周三在墨尔本公园四分之一决赛中对阵德国选手亚历山大·兹维列夫，这无疑将面临澳大利亚网球公开赛中最严峻的考验，这场比赛有望成为一场精彩的风格冲突。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:07:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tennis-alcaraz-gears-up-zverev-examination-melbourne-2024-01-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>